@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title The three governance bodies as checks and balances

[Constitutional Committee\n(CC)\nchecks constitutionality] as CC
[Delegated Representatives\n(DReps)\nvoice of ADA holders] as DR
[Stake Pool Operators\n(SPOs)\nhard forks + some params] as SPO

rectangle "Governance action" as GA

DR --> GA : vote (most types)
CC --> GA : vote (constitutionality)
SPO --> GA : vote (hard fork, security params)

note bottom of GA
  Each of the seven action types needs a
  different mix of these three bodies to
  meet its ratification thresholds.
end note
@enduml
